dashboardDefaults.emptyCalendarTitleText: It looks like you do not have any filings for the next 12 months. Check back later.
dashboardDefaults.emptyCalendarBodyText: If you are an LLC, C Corp, LP, or LLP, you need to tell us your business formation date so we can tell you when your next filing is due. You can do this by [updating your profile](#).
dashboardDefaults.calendarLegalText: This calendar is not a complete list of your obligations as a business.
dashboardDefaults.calendarTooltip: This calendar shows you New Jersey tax and reporting due dates unique to your business. Click on any item to learn where to file.
